{{Campaignbox 科索沃战争}}

1999年3月27日，在[[北约轰炸南斯拉夫|北约轰炸南斯拉夫]]期间，南斯拉夫武装力量{{Le|第250防空导弹旅|250th Air Defense Missile Brigade}}使用[[SA-3导弹|SA-3地对空导弹]]击落了美军一架[[F-117夜鷹戰鬥攻擊機|F-117A“夜鹰”]]。机上的美军飞行员成功弹射逃生，获[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]救起。<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/264045596|publisher=Schiffer Military History|date=2009|location=Atglen, PA|isbn=978-0-7643-3242-5|oclc=264045596|first=Don|last=Logan|title=Lockheed F-117 Night Hawks : a stealth fighter roll call|access-date=2021-02-20|archive-date=2021-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210220132411/https://www.worldcat.org/title/lockheed-f-117-night-hawks-a-stealth-fighter-roll-call/oclc/264045596|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Rescue of Vega 31|url=https://www.defensemedianetwork.com/stories/the-rescue-of-vega-31-how-special-ops-forces-saved-an-f-117-pilot-in-serbia/|accessdate=2021-02-20|author=Robert F. Dorr|work=Defense Media Network|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123256/https://www.defensemedianetwork.com/stories/the-rescue-of-vega-31-how-special-ops-forces-saved-an-f-117-pilot-in-serbia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>事故中的F-117A战机装备精良，是当时第一架围绕[[低可偵測性技術|隐形技术]]设计的战机，而南斯拉夫防空系统则被认为过时。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title="Pilot recognizes crashed F-117A|url=http://usatoday.com/news/index/kosovo/koso096.htm|publisher=USA Today|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990910071026/http://usatoday.com/news/index/kosovo/koso096.htm|archivedate=1999-09-10|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2021-02-20}}</ref>

==袭击过程==
本次袭击的执行部队是南斯拉夫武装力量第250防空导弹旅，指挥官为{{Le|佐尔坦·达尼|Zoltán Dani}}，使用的武器为SA-3导弹。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Air Defense: How to Take Down an F-117|url=https://www.strategypage.com/htmw/htada/articles/20051121.aspx|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=www.strategypage.com|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106030502/https://www.strategypage.com/htmw/htada/articles/20051121.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>被击落的战机注册编号为82-0806，呼号Vega 31。<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Who shot down F-117A?|url=http://www.defenceaviation.com/2007/02/how-was-f-117-shot-down-part-2.html|author=Dsouza, Larkins|date=2007-02-08|publisher=Defense Aviation|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415224243/http://www.defenceaviation.com/2007/02/how-was-f-117-shot-down-part-2.html|archivedate=2009-04-15|accessdate=2021-02-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

Zoltán Dani上校在得知战争开始后的数小时后，即带领第250地空导弹旅第三营开始战术机动，并成功维持其导弹营完好无损，直至战争结束。在离开原驻地30分钟后，原驻地即遭北约轰炸，Zoltán Dani上校一行在远处目睹了驻地被炸。后来，Zoltán Dani上校经计算后认为，其导弹营的搜索雷达每次开机时间不能超过20秒，否则即会被北约反辐射系统定位，因此在机动的大部分时间里都应保持无线电静默。期间仅通过部署一些观察员，通过目视来寻找北约战机（一开始并未特别关注F-117）的作战规律。基于观察总结的北约机轰炸规律，其导弹营在北约机轰炸贝尔格莱德的必经之路上设伏。根据观察和当晚贝尔格莱德被轰炸的时间报告，于间隙性短暂雷达搜索中，在当地时间1999年3月27日20时15分时，第250地空导弹旅以13公里的半径发射了对空导弹。根据炮手乔治·安尼契奇回忆，部队发现23公里内有F-117战机的踪迹，为了避免被北约军队的[[對敵防空壓制|防空压制系统]]锁定，南联盟军队用了不到17秒操作发射导弹。

被击落的F-117A战机上的飞行员是美国空军中校达热尔·帕特里克·泽尔科<ref name=":1" />，他和他所驾驶的战机都曾参加[[海湾战争|海湾战争]]<ref>Dorr, Robert F. "USAF Fighter Force at 60". ''AirForces Monthly magazine'', October 2007</ref><ref name="N2007">{{cite journal | url=http://f117sfa.org/sfa_newsletter/Newsletter2007-05.pdf | title=Interview with Lt Colonel Dale Zelko, USAF | journal=Nighthawks | date=May 2007 | volume=5 | issue=1 | publisher=F-117 Stealth Fighter Association | access-date=2015-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043205/http://f117sfa.org/sfa_newsletter/Newsletter2007-05.pdf | archive-date=2016-03-04 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他发现两枚导弹穿透低空的云层，直奔战机而来。第一枚导弹从他身旁擦过，距离近到使飞机产生抖振，但没有爆炸；第二枚则在战机附近爆炸，冲击波损坏了战机，令其失去控制。<ref name="N2007" />爆炸的景象大到从[[波斯尼亞地區|波斯尼亚地区]]上空飞过的[[KC-135空中加油机|KC-135空中加油机]]都能看到。<ref name="N2007" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Serb discusses 1999 downing of stealth|url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-10-26-serb-stealth_x.htm|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=USA Today|archive-date=2012-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713144045/http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-10-26-serb-stealth_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

泽尔科受到巨大的[[G力|G力]]冲击，难以找对弹射的姿势。展开降落伞后，他不像受训时落地后求救<ref>{{Cite web|title=Audio From The 1999 Shoot Down Of F-117 "Vega 31" Over Serbia Is Chilling|url=https://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/13766/audio-from-the-1999-shoot-down-of-f-117-vega-31-over-serbia-is-chilling|accessdate=2021-02-20|last=Rogoway|first=Tyler|work=The Drive|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000606/https://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/13766/audio-from-the-1999-shoot-down-of-f-117-vega-31-over-serbia-is-chilling|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在空中下落时就用无线电求救，发出[[Mayday|Mayday]]信号，得到了目击爆炸的加油机的回应<ref name="N2007" />。关于在空中求救一事，泽尔科解释称高处的信号更好，而且他确信自己一旦落地就会被南斯拉夫俘虏，他想在被逮捕之前确认自己没有受伤。

泽尔科在[[伏伊伏丁那|伏伊伏丁那]]自治省[[魯馬|鲁马]]以南的一处田地落地，离战机坠毁的地点不到一[[英里|英里]]，稍往北就是[[欧洲E30公路|欧洲E30公路]]。他躲在一条水沟中，感受到[[B-2幽灵战略轰炸机|B-2轰炸机]]投下炸弹的音波。<ref name="N2007" />南斯拉夫军民展开大搜捕，最近时离他藏身的水沟只有几百米。3月28日凌晨，驾驶[[MH-53直升机|MH-53直升机]]的美军{{Le|战场搜救|Combat search and rescue}}人员成功救起泽尔科。泽尔科后来得知，在原地再待几分钟就会被南斯拉夫军队俘虏。<ref name="N2007" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Stranger Who Changed My Life: My Enemy, My Friend|url=https://www.rd.com/article/the-stranger-who-changed-my-life-my-enemy-my-friend/|accessdate=2021-02-20|date=2013-11-12|work=Reader's Digest|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217180843/https://www.rd.com/article/the-stranger-who-changed-my-life-my-enemy-my-friend/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1999年5月2日，第250防空导弹旅又击落了一架美军[[F-16戰隼戰鬥機|F-16战机]]，其飞行员是后来的[[美国空军参谋长|美国空军参谋长]]——[[大卫·戈德费因|大卫·戈德费因]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Holloman commander recalls being shot down in Serbia|url=https://www.f-16.net/f-16-news-article2167.html|accessdate=2021-02-20|date=2007-02-07|work=www.f-16.net|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208001443/https://www.f-16.net/f-16-news-article2167.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Airframe Details for F-16 #88-0550|url=https://www.f-16.net/aircraft-database/F-16/airframe-profile/2787|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=www.f-16.net|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128104702/http://www.f-16.net/aircraft-database/F-16/airframe-profile/2787/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=USAF F-16CG crashes over Yugoslavia|url=https://www.f-16.net/f-16-news-article214.html|accessdate=2021-02-20|author=Lieven Dewitte|date=1999-05-01|work=www.f-16.net|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220045806/http://www.f-16.net/f-16-news-article214.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==后续发展==
现场照片显示，F-117A战机倒着卡在地里，机身没有太多损坏。<ref name=":0" />美军决定不回收销毁战机残骸。F-117战机基于1970年代的技术制造，美军则在1980年代对外披露它的存在，彼时的[[航展|航展]]上常有它的身影。美国空军上将{{Le|布鲁斯·卡尔森|Bruce A. Carlson}}推测，如果塞尔维亚把残骸交给俄罗斯，机身的损害会最小。<ref>{{Cite web|title=When Secrets Crash|url=https://www.airforcemag.com/article/0701crash/|accessdate=2021-02-20|author=Jeffrey T. Richelson|date=2001-07|work=Air Force Magazine|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107194112/https://www.airforcemag.com/article/0701crash/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[航空博物館_(貝爾格勒)|贝尔格莱德航空博物馆]]收藏了一些F-117A的碎片<ref>{{Cite web|title=Air Museum, Belgrade, Serbia by Vlada Marinkovic|url=https://pbase.com/vmarinkovic/air_museum|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=PBase|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902215735/https://www.pbase.com/vmarinkovic/air_museum|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有媒体报道其他碎片流到中俄两国，用于两国发展防隐身技术<ref>{{Cite web|title=Russia Offers India $8 Billion Weapons Deal|url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20011213031937/http://www.newsmax.com/archives/articles/2001/12/12/140853.shtml|accessdate=2021-02-20|author=Smith, Charles R|date=2001-12-12|publisher=newsmax|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901071137/http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20011213031937/http%3A//www.newsmax.com/archives/articles/2001/12/12/140853.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。机身的一点橡胶部分则在北约和南联盟战争期间由塞尔维亚军事家[[傑利科·拉茲尼亞托維奇|傑利科·拉茲尼亞托維奇]]赠送给西方记者。<ref>{{Cite web|title=MOGU DA POLOMIM F-117A: Evo kako je ARKAN uništio ponos Amerike i "nevidljivi" bombarder! (VIDEO)|url=https://www.telegraf.rs/vesti/politika/1496575-mogu-da-polomim-f-117a-evo-kako-je-arkan-unistio-ponos-amerike-i-nevidljivi-bombarder-video|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=Telegraf.rs|language=sr|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119143753/https://www.telegraf.rs/vesti/politika/1496575-mogu-da-polomim-f-117a-evo-kako-je-arkan-unistio-ponos-amerike-i-nevidljivi-bombarder-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，美国空军所属的所有F-117战机退役。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stealth fighters fly off the radar|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2008-apr-23-fi-stealth23-story.html|accessdate=2021-02-20|date=2008-04-23|last=Pae|first=Peter|work=Los Angeles Times|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722030926/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/apr/23/business/fi-stealth23|dead-url=no}}</ref>

时光流逝，佐尔坦·达尼转行开起面包店，而泽尔科也离开了部队。两人2011年见面，自此成为了好友。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Foes now friends: US stealth pilot and the Serb who shot him down|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-20209770|newspaper=BBC News|date=2012-11-06|accessdate=2021-02-20|language=en-GB|quote=(T)hey worked towards a face-to-face encounter. That finally came last year.|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204001323/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-20209770|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年，一名F-117A飞行员表示，他的僚机在1999年的击落事件后遭到南斯拉夫[[地对空导弹|地对空导弹]]击中，但战机成功返回了基地。此次攻击的详情仍然保密，只有一点细节得以公布。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Yes, Serbian Air Defenses Did Hit Another F-117 During Operation Allied Force In 1999|url=https://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/37894/yes-serbian-air-defenses-did-hit-another-f-117-during-operation-allied-force-in-1999|accessdate=2021-02-20|last=Newdick|first=Thomas|work=The Drive|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216053455/https://www.thedrive.com/the-war-zone/37894/yes-serbian-air-defenses-did-hit-another-f-117-during-operation-allied-force-in-1999|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=DRAGANOVA MIRNA RUKA DOKRAJČILA I DRUGOG "NEVIDLJIVOG": Pripadnici Trećeg diviziona 250. brigade PVO o podvigu tokom NATO bombardovanja|url=https://www.novosti.rs/vesti/drustvo/942347/draganova-mirna-ruka-dokrajcila-drugog-nevidljivog-pripadnici-treceg-diviziona-250-brigade-pvo-podvigu-tokom-nato-bombardovanja|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=NOVOSTI|language=sr|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103102533/https://www.novosti.rs/vesti/drustvo/942347/draganova-mirna-ruka-dokrajcila-drugog-nevidljivog-pripadnici-treceg-diviziona-250-brigade-pvo-podvigu-tokom-nato-bombardovanja|dead-url=no}}</ref>

